In the pre-holiday frenzy with the added drama at Sotheby's, I=E2=80=99d
only glanced at this odd New York Times story ( https://www.nytimes.com/202=
4/12/17/arts/design/van-gogh-lost-masterpiece.html?utm_campaign=3DWall+Powe=
r+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F5%2F25%29&utm_content=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%28=
