=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) identifying=E2=80=94sort of=E2=80=94the family that=
 now owns the storied 1890 van Gogh painting, Portrait of Dr. Gachet. This =
was one of the last works made by the artist, and its purchase marked the p=
eak of the Japanese art-buying frenzy of the late 1980s and into early 1990=
, when it was
auctioned at Christie=E2=80=99s for $82.5 million ($204.3 million in today=
=E2=80=99s dollars).=C2=A0

=C2=A0

I=E2=80=99m not sure the Times understands that outing the very discreet It=
alian-Swiss family that probably owns the painting=E2=80=94they didn=E2=80=
=99t deny it through their lawyers=E2=80=94isn=E2=80=99t really news. If th=
e family decides to sell, that=E2=80=99s a story. But owning a major van Go=
gh for nearly 30 years, and never letting anyone see
it, creates the sort of mystique that makes some works of art so valuable.=
=C2=A0

=C2=A0

The far more interesting part of the painting=E2=80=99s provenance concerns=
 the man who owned the work briefly in the late 1990s=E2=80=94but never saw=
 it. Wolfgang Fl=C3=B6ttl, the now-disgraced Austrian hedge fund manager, l=
ived a dangerous financial life built upon secretly borrowed money and soci=
al climbing. (The
Wall Street Journal published ( https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB116186493590=
604582?utm_campaign=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F5%2F25%29&utm_content=
=3DWall+Power+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2812%2F22%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&ut=
m_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) a good overview in 2=
007, when Fl=C3=B6ttl=E2=80=99s scheme unraveled.) Before then, in 1997, Fl=
=C3=B6ttl had been acquiring art partially funded by credit from Sotheby=E2=
=80=99s. When he bought the van Gogh, his debt to Sotheby=E2=80=99s balloon=
ed to $240 million. He couldn=E2=80=99t make payments in the wake of the Lo=
ng-Term Capital collapse, however, and Sotheby=E2=80=99s started selling hi=
s
paintings. That=E2=80=99s how Portrait of Dr. Gachet wound up in Switzerlan=
d=E2=80=A6 or wherever it is.=C2=A0

