uela is designed to serve as =E2=80=9Ca democratic space that doesn=E2=80=
=99t feel like it has the pomp and ceremony that some places have,=E2=80=9D=
 <strong>Bee Emmott</strong>, the C.E.O. of Artfarm, Hauser=E2=80=99s siste=
r hospitality company,
