ly, Hauser &amp; Wirth is building a potentially valuable business off
the untapped resource of the gallery=E2=80=99s stable of artists, estates, =
and their inventory.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=
=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">At Manuela, as at other Art=
