tly what you would
expect=E2=80=A6 a mid-career survey of localish seasonal eateries.=E2=80=9D=
=C2=A0=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">The New York Manuela serves a different fu=
